PIP SSL problem : https://github.com/pypa/pip/issues/5226

Link Tutorial : https://tecadmin.net/install-django-on-debian/

1. sudo apt-get install python3 python3-pip

2. python3 -V

3. pip3 -V

4. pip3 install Django

5. django-admin --version

Step 3 – Create Django Application

6. django-admin startproject django_app

7. cd django_app 

8. python3 manage.py migrate

Step 4 – Create Super Admin Account

9. python3 manage.py createsuperuser

Step 5 – Run Django Application

10. vi django_app/settings.py

11. python3 manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8000

